Ibikorwa by'ubwandu bwa Coronavirus (COVID-19) byerekana ko hari ibintu bimwe na bimwe bibaho hagati y'ibihugu by'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'u Burayi, bigatuma icyorezo cya COVID-19 gitera imbere mu bihugu byose, nubwo kiri mu byiciro bitandukanye bitewe n'igihugu.
Hashingiwe ku bumenyi buva mu Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bukomeye bigomba kurushaho kwitegura ko abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho mu buryo bwihuse, cyane cyane mu buryo bwihariye, kugira ngo bagire imibereho myiza.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa, havuzwe icyorezo cya PN, gifitwe n'ibitekerezo by'uburwayi bitamenyekanye.
Ku itariki ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko Coronavirus nshya ikomeje kwitwa Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) kuko ari yo ifite akamaro.
Niyo mpamvu indwara yatewe no kwandura SARS-CoV-2 yise Coronavirus Disease (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu amakuru yemewe ni uko 80% by'abanduye COVID-19 baba bafite uburwayi bworoheje, ni ukuvuga ubwandu bw'imyenda yo mu kirere, haba mu maraso cyangwa badafite nimoniya, kandi abenshi muri bo bakira.
