Ubushakashatsi bwo mu 2013 bwagaragaje ko imyitwarire myiza yo gukaraba intoki ishobora gutuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu bagenda barushaho gukura, bakagira amajyambere make.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, guhinduranya imyitwarire yoroheje nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune bishobora kugabanya umubare w'abana bapfa bazize indwara z'ubuhumekero n'izitera indwara z'urusoro.
Iyi gahunda yoroheje ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa bazize iyo ndwara ku kigero cya 50%.
