Uretse kwirinda kutabona ubwandu bwa mbere, uburyo bwo kugenzura impanuka ku bagize uwo muryango burimo gukoresha imashini z'imyuka, abarinzi b'imyanya y'ubuhumekero, n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite mu gihe umuntu arwaye COVID-19 ahanganye n'ibiza.
