BAnziotensin-converter enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni ingirabuzimafatizo ihura n'ibihaha, umutima, impyiko n'indwara zo mu nda.
ACE2 irwanya ingirabuzima fatizo ihindura angiotensin (ACE) ikora ibi binyuze mu kugabanya ingano ya angiotensin-II no kongera ang1-7), bigatuma iba umuti wizeza kuvurira indwara z'umutima. ACE2 ikora nk'ikirindiro cy'ingirabuzima fatizo zimwe na zimwe za coronavirus.
Igitabo cyitwa The Human Version of the Enzyme (Ibitabo byitwa The Human Version of the Enzyme) cyitwa hACE2.
Ingirabuzimafatizo ihindura angiotensin 2 ni ingirabuzimafatizo ihindura zinc ibera ku gice cyo mu gice cy'umubiri cy'ingirabuzimafatizo n'ibindi bice by'umubiri.
Proth√©ine ACE2 ifite umurongo wa N-terminal peptidease M2 n'umurongo wa C-terminal colectrine renal amino acid transporter.
ACE2 ni poroteyine yo mu gice cy'umubiri cy'umubiri cy'uburyo bumwe, ifite umwanya usanzwe ukorwa n'ibinyabuzima mu mihumeka no mu bindi bice by'umubiri.
Urubuga rw'ibanze rwa ACE2 rutandukanywa n'urundi ruhare rw'ingingo zitwara abantu, ari rwo shade, bigatuma proteine ihoraho ihinduka umuti mu maraso, ikajya mu mazi.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifitanye isano cyane n'uruhu rw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso z'indwara ya Alviolase yo mu bwoko bwa II, interocyte zo mu nda ntoya, ingirabuzimafatizo zo mu ngingo nyinshi z'amaraso n'amaraso, n'ingirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso z'uruhu rw'amaraso.
Hari n'ubwoko bw'inyamaswa z'ibinyabuzima (ACE2 mRNA) mu bice by'umubiri (Cerebral Cortex, Stretum, Hypothylumus, and Brainstemes).
Icy'ibanze cya ACE2 ni uko gifasha mu gutuma ACE igenda itera.
ACE ingiotensin I ihindura homone ya angiotensin II ikora ubushakashatsi ku bintu by'umubiri.
ACE2 itandukanya aminiyo asidi ya carboxylate-terminal phenylalanine (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) na angiotensin II, ikayihindura hydrolyzed mu gisindisha cy'umurava (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora gutandukanya andi peptide amwe n'amwe, harimo [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A na ghrelin.
ACE2 ihindagura imiterere y'urwangizi rwa SLC6A19, ikora nk'umushinga wa amino acid, kandi ishobora gutuma umutima utera.
Kubera ko ACE2 ari poroteyine yo mu gice cy'umubiri, ikora nk'ikirindiro cy'ingirabuzimafatizo mu gihe cy'indwara zimwe na zimwe za coronavirus, zirimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi ikora SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi ikora COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, mu rwego rw'ingingo z'ingenzi za ACE2, SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 bifatirwa ku gice cy'ingirabuzimafatizo, bigatuma endocytosis igenda ihindagurika, ndetse bikagaragaza ko virusi na enzymes byombi bigahindukira mu bice by'ingirabuzimafatizo biri hagati y'ingirabuzimafatizo.
