Iyi porogaramu yashyizweho n'itsinda ry'ikoranabuhanga ryo mu karere, yashyizwe ahagaragara nk'isoko ry'amakuru, kandi izashyikirizwa guverinoma. Macedonia ya Ruguru Hagarira Coronavirus!, porogaramu ishingiye kuri Bluetooth yashyizweho igamije kumenya ibimenyetso by'abantu bashobora kuba banduye no gutanga igisubizo gisanzwe ku nzego z'ubuzima.
