Ariko, Ikigo cy'ubuvuzi bw'amaraso cya Wuhan, mu gihe cyatangaza ko umuntu agomba guhabwa dosiye y'umugera wa buri mudugudu ku munsi, kivuga ko inshuro ebyiri z'iyo dosiye zishobora guteza akaga gakomeye kandi ko zishobora kwica.
Ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yemeje ko habaho gukoresha byihutirwa Hydroxychloroquine na Chloruquine ku bushake bw'abaganga bagenzura abantu banduye COVID-19. Mu mabwiriza yo mu gitabo cya 7 cy'Amashyaka y'Ubushinwa, harimo interferon, ribavirin cyangwa umufenovir mu gihe COVID-19 ikomeje kugaragara.
Amakuru y'ibanze agaragaza ko dosiye nyinshi za Ribavirin zikenewe mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 mu vitro.
Nitasexanide yagiriwe inama yo gukora ubushakashatsi kuri VIVO nyuma yo kugaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubukana buke. Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gutegura poroteyine ya spike y'ibanze na Transmembrane Protease Serine 2 (TMPRSS2) ari ngombwa kugira ngo SARS-CoV-2 yinjire binyuze mu guhuza na ACE2 receptor.
Ubushakashatsi ku cyitwa chlorokine na hydroxychloroquine, haba ku azithromycin cyangwa ntayo, bufite imipaka ikomeye yatumye abaganga batemera ubu buvuzi, nta n'ubwo bwarushaho kubikora.
Icyiciro cya nyuma cya COVID-19 gikomeye gishobora gutuma icyago cya cytokine kiba ikibazo gikomeye.
Hari ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira icyuho cyo kureka kurekura cyotokini vuba. Nyuma yo kurangiza ikigo gito, Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima mu Bushinwa yashyize Tosillizumab mu mabwiriza y'ubuvuzi.
Iki kigo kiri mu cyiciro cya 2 cy'igeragezwa ritagira ingano ku rwego rw'igihugu mu Butaliyani nyuma yo kubona ibisubizo byiza mu bantu barwaye indwara ikomeye.
Gufata amaraso hamwe na serum feritine mu rwego rwo kumenya icyago cya cytokine bisobanura gukumira uburwayi, ibyo bikaba byemeza ko ari byo byateje urupfu rw'abantu bamwe na bamwe bafite icyo cyorezo.
Mu 2017, interleukin-6 receptor antagonist FDA yemeje ko CAR T cell therapy ari umuti w'uburwayi bw'ibanze, ku buryo ishobora kuvura indwara z'ibikomere.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya igaragara, igenga, y'uko Tocilizumab ari umuti mwiza wa CRS.
Abakize COVID-19 barimo gushakishwa uburyo bw'ubwirinzi butariho urukingo bwo guha abakize imiti ikoreshwa n'umubiri wabo kandi ikoreshwa cyane n'umubiri wabo.
Iyi ngamba yageragejwe SARS, ariko nta cyo byatangaje.
Guhumeka virusi ni uburyo bwihariye bwitezwe ko imiti ya antibody itagira icyo ikora ishobora guhuza ubwirinzi kuri SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko kandi, ubundi buryo nk'ubufasha bwa cytototoxicity ya porogaramu ya interineti, na/cyangwa fagositose, bushobora kuba bushoboka.
